Coliseum Poker is a Progressive Jackpot video poker! To win the jackpot you need to place the maximum bet of 5 coins per game and get Royal Flush combination. The game is played with a 52-card deck. Once a player places a bet of one or more credits, he is dealt five cards. The player chooses which of 5 cards he wants to hold and which to discard. The cards discarded are replaced with new ones from the deck. The objective is to get the best-paying winning hand.